{"tid":1451122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷靜！冷靜！冷靜！","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:42:31.000Z","uid":294431,"like":13,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"085d4f5226dc2d569c21f97d1a7055e09dbf2c42","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"我知道呢一刻大家都好嬲！！！<br />\n但係，係咁嬲嘅情況底下就更加要冷靜一下！<br />\n所有事情都要有計劃先至會做得出成效，<br />\n無論你係勇武定還是係和理非，<br />\n呢一刻盡量平復自己心情，<br />\n然後開始動員身邊嘅所有人，<br />\n我哋必須要反擊！<br />\n但係一定要有計劃咁行事！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷靜！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"367f8bbd1455cfd758177d41755dcdcd4494bee4","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:23:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"97aeb19e7c354637932248b9046ea9e37319f1f5","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:23:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"dcbcbd55550f88dddcedb8f0cd9c573c194d1fd2","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:23:37.000Z","msg":"要反擊"},{"pid":"eb940c4554018dab9f6d4bdf31686c794fd2d3d8","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"不過要計劃"},{"pid":"e6e93540ba95e24966dbf4e0a825cc01be7df56f","tid":1451122,"uid":98842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:23:58.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\nTG群組，不停轉發出去，勢要討回雙眼，嬲到火屎呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群好多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=1432e3b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=cf090efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n不要說推<br />\n試著說812機場見"},{"pid":"a7a49ec1baaee7c98f749cba29d18bcae3fa72ba","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:01.000Z","msg":"唔好魯莽"},{"pid":"04c91317721198804ff2adce308cbe5ffebfc7d0","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"冷靜"},{"pid":"a24f3e7a4155ace96606d12ebe16979260eb356d","tid":1451122,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:25.000Z","msg":"冷靜？"},{"pid":"50d138749a62d3b25438629bfd371d427120c77f","tid":1451122,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以眼還眼 黑警死全家！<br />\n心態改變命運<br />\n人數決定一切<br />\n<br />\n你 班 仆 街 幾 時 先 肯 無 限 期 四 罷？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450867</a><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"80a9498b92f0a7871613ab01635f1e2fcf784fed","tid":1451122,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f00a19768ff7a745cb8467e6f7cc970d6d7a021d","tid":1451122,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:41.000Z","msg":"唔好推垃圾post<br />\n推返行動post"},{"pid":"5dddda27469bea99aa63d689d3ccdf2d5a188b21","tid":1451122,"uid":165750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:06.000Z","msg":"我好冷靜咁講<br />\n<br />\n聽日塞爆機場離境大堂<br />\n<br />\n你去就去，唔去就收聲幫手做文宣"},{"pid":"f0097026255ff30cbbd4e558384a0141de5acb90","tid":1451122,"uid":148390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:09.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅繼續做<br />\n<br />\n唔敢勇武嘅同我一齊屌<br />\n<br />\n希望全民和應 靠把口令警犬崩潰 「屌狗老母」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449909</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de83beb86da0e7d3e0b8472e3ecad1f98a8f0c59","tid":1451122,"uid":294431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dddda27469bea99aa63d689d3ccdf2d5a188b21","tid":1451122,"uid":165750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:06.000Z","msg":"我好冷靜咁講<br />\n<br />\n聽日塞爆機場離境大堂<br />\n<br />\n你去就去，唔去就收聲幫手做文宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"去！<br />\n我指緊其他行動要計劃！"},{"pid":"0be1208bd3b9c74f07d20bcb30e3c7a3caea9e10","tid":1451122,"uid":149183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4DqZYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4DqZYz.jpg&h=20236277&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w04Ra5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw04Ra5f.jpg&h=a69f6a03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/